longBusinessSummary: Devin Energy Corporation, an exploration stage company, focuses on the acquisition, exploration, and development of oil and gas properties in the United States. The company holds an 8.56% interest in the Siggins Oil Mining Project #1 located in Cumberland County, Illinois. Devin Energy Corporation is based in Sumner, Illinois.
